Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:49.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里本斯终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.00,0:17:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Memento-Mori的使用…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.25,0:17:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就能加速中东计划…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类的意志也能够得以统一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.88,0:17:58.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,统一?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.64,0:18:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是应该说被统一吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是统一哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.68,0:18:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说都会聚集到我们这边而来的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对于Memento-Mori的建造协助
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.69,0:18:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很感谢你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.94,0:18:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.53,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变革者们创造出来的未来…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.62,0:18:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟!
