Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:34.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约翰哥的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你把兄长们…!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:38.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 原来如此么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就觉得在哪遇到过
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来是那时候的小姑娘么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.89,0:18:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一下子这么有女人味了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.89,0:18:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这混蛋!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想和我对着干么?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.60,0:18:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别乱来哦 难得捡回来的小命…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.82,0:18:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又会不保的哦
