Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.08,0:19:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各部分连接 没有异常哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.46,0:19:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好~ 刹那
